Htmls:
The websites are located on the storage so you can use this application offline.

Instalation:
To run the program you have to install python 3 (or newer versions).

Windows -

1. Go to python.org/downloads/
2. Download python for Windows
3. Run The instalation program

Linux -

1. open Terminal
2. $ sudo apt-get install software-properties-common
3. $ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:deadsnakes/ppa
4. $ sudo apt-get update
5. $ sudo apt-get install python3.8

Utilization:

1. Open a console window in the Problem Solver '(Version 0.1 Beta)' folder.
2. $ python3 main.py
